race.description: Gallopers Sports Club Qtis 3YO Maiden Plate
race.comment: TACITLY (6) hit the frame at Scone on debut before being tipped out for further time to furnish. Has since returned just missing the placings at Randwick and should appreciate the drop back in company here. Sure to be right there when the whips are cracking. ARTISTIC ENDEAVOUR (2) has placed over this distance range and will be rock-hard fit for this. Gets some weight relief with the claim and can make his presence felt. RED SAMOVAR (10) wasn't too far away at the Sunny Coast last time out and must be respected from the Vandyke barn. Top-three contender. ENJECTOR (5) looks to be improving with racing and maps ideally from gate three. In the mix. DASHING MARS (4) next in line.
